sequenceDiagram
    participant O as Orchestrator<br/>span: root
    participant KP as Kafka Producer
    participant KT as Kafka Topic<br/>agent.tasks.summarizer
    participant KC as Kafka Consumer<br/>(Summarizer)
    participant S as Summarizer<br/>span: child-1
    participant MA as Mistral Adapter<br/>span: child-2

    Note over O: Create root span<br/>trace_id=abc123, span_id=0001
    O->>KP: produce message
    Note over KP: inject headers:<br/>traceparent: 00-abc123-0001-01
    KP->>KT: message + trace headers

    KT->>KC: deliver message
    Note over KC: extract traceparent header<br/>create child span<br/>trace_id=abc123, span_id=0002<br/>parent_span_id=0001

    KC->>S: process task
    Note over S: child span active<br/>span_id=0002

    S->>MA: A2A POST /tasks<br/>W3C traceparent header
    Note over MA: child span<br/>span_id=0003, parent=0002

    MA-->>S: TaskResponse
    Note over MA: close span 0003

    S->>KP: produce result
    Note over KP: inject headers:<br/>traceparent: 00-abc123-0002-01

    KP->>O: result message
    Note over O: continue root span<br/>full trace: 0001 → 0002 → 0003
